        "description": "<p>This Plugin changes the &#8216;freshness &#8216; that bbPress displays on topic and forum lists (eg 4 hours ago) to the date of the last post to that forum or topic (eg 17th January 2014 at 5.15pm).<\/p>\n<p>It also allows you to set the heading for this new date format.<\/p>\n<p>The existing (bbpress) Recent Topics widget works with date, but a revised Recent Replies Widget to display the date format called (Last Post) Recent Replies is included.<\/p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Go to Dashboard&gt;plugins&gt;add new<\/li>\n<li>Search for &#8216;bbp last post&#8217;<\/li>\n<li>Click install<\/li>\n<li>and then activate<\/li>\n<li>To set the heading &#8211; go to Dashboard&gt;settings&gt;bbp last post and follow the instructions to select what heading to display.<\/li>\n<li>If you are using the (bbPress) Replies widget, go to Dashboard&gt;appearance&gt;widgets, remove your existing &#8216;(bbPress) Recent Replies&#8217; widget, and replace with the &#8216;(Last Post) Recent Replies&#8217; Widget<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<p>1.7 german translation added<br \/>\n1.6 small amendment to gettext filter to atch in $text<br \/>\n1.5 amend to allow filters on functions and revised getext filter<br \/>\n1.4 amend functions line 7 to take out undefined varaible error<br \/>\n1.3 internationization phase 2 &#8211; correct date not displaying<br \/>\n1.2 internationalization<br \/>\n1.1 correction to topic freshness bug<br \/>\n1.0 Version 1<\/p>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/bbp-last-post\/trunk\/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=3066382\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/bbp-last-post\/trunk\/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=3066382\" alt=\"The display before this plugin\"><\/a><p>The display before this plugin<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/bbp-last-post\/trunk\/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=3066382\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/bbp-last-post\/trunk\/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=3066382\" alt=\"The display after this plugin\"><\/a><p>The display after this plugin<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/bbp-last-post\/trunk\/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=3066382\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/bbp-last-post\/trunk\/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=3066382\" alt=\"The settings page\"><\/a><p>The settings page<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/bbp-last-post\/trunk\/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=3066382\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/bbp-last-post\/trunk\/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=3066382\" alt=\"The (last Post) Recent Replies Widget\"><\/a><p>The (last Post) Recent Replies Widget<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Nice and usefull plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/igorpedro\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/fdf609eac4a61219762a251992fcc702?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/fdf609eac4a61219762a251992fcc702?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/igorpedro\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Igor <small>(igorpedro)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 4, 2020<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin solved my problem with the date format of the BBPress recent replies widget<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/stef06\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/63f8572205fb3c90dd2d9451b5b7eece?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/63f8572205fb3c90dd2d9451b5b7eece?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/stef06\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">stef06<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 22, 2019<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">perfect <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very happy, it works perfectly<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/treeflips\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/4971d79a5e73c08a0b4229c42f9be9fa?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/4971d79a5e73c08a0b4229c42f9be9fa?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar a